c: 4
v: 77
t: "E a yi'aali Й“en wi'ananooЙ“e : \"Suree juuЙ—e mon Й—en, Гұimnon julde, jonnon asakal\". Tuma hare nden farlanoo e maЙ“Й“e, e jaka fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e hino hulira yimЙ“e Й“en wano Alla hulirtee, maa ko Й“uri tiiЙ—ude e kulol, Й“e wi'i: \"Joomi amen, ko honЙ—um FarlaЙ—aa e dow amen hare ? Ko haЙ—noo Nennitanaa men Й—um haa e lajal Й“adiingal ?\" Maaku : \"Dakamme aduna on ko seeЙ—a, ko laakara on Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on hulЙ—o [Alla], on tooГұetaake yeru hufol tamara"